item.title: Change We Can Believe In Pt. 3
item.dc:creator: import
item.description: In the midst of so many distractions, it's so easy to subject to the standards lowered by our culture. However, Scripture teaches us that the church ought not conform to the patterns or philosophies of the world, but to be renewed by the tranforming of our minds. As much as change can often frighten us, it isn't always bad. Join us this week as Pastor Jared shares an encouraging message on how change is worth anticipating. Download Audio Download Video
